00118 typedef struct _node
00119 {
00120   short type;                   /* token type */
00121   union
00122   {
00123     ITintmax scalar;            /* scalar value */
00124     double real;                /* floating point value */
00125     char *string;               /* string */
00126     struct _node *child;        /* child list */
00127   }
00128   value;
00129   struct _node *sibling;        /* sibling */
00130   /* BCC - used for long lists */
00131   struct _node *last_child;     /* last child */
00132 }
00133 NODE, *LIST;
